2015-03-03  Simon J. Gerraty  <sjg@bad.crufty.net>

	* install-mk (MK_VERSION): 20150303
	
	* dirdeps.mk: if MK_DIRDEPS_CACHE is yes, use dirdeps-cache
	  which is built via sub-make so we have a .meta file to tell if
	  it is out-of-date. 
